    Scope and Contents
The Student Services/Financial Aid working papers file consists of collection agency information from 1976; Sangamon State University College Work Study Program and financial aid reports from the early 70's.  Also includes Illinois State Scholarship Commission-composite payment listings, 1970-78; ISSC purpose of statement, plus information on National Defense/Direct Student Loan Programs at SSU, and maintenance of level records for FY 1971, 72 and 73.  The files were extensively weeded; several computer printouts of awards to individual students were shredded.  
  
